      "title": "Latest announcement on functioning of schools next week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Schools in suburbs, which remained closed last week, will function as per usual on Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday next week, the Ministry of Education announces.",
        "According to a statement issued by the ministry, primary sections of these schools will function at the discretion of respective principals."
